                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940430-23-defend258 t17940430-23-punish121"></join>
               Fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Baron THOMPSON.</p>
